  "text": "To every vector field X on M one can also associate a R n -valued functionX on Q defined byX(u) := u −1 X π(u) . The connection α induces a covariant derivative ∇ α on TM which satisfies [CITATION_1] (∇ α X Y ) π(u) = u(X(Ŷ )) for every vector fields X, Y on M and u ∈ Q (see [CITATION_2] , Lemma on p. 115).",
